You will stop along the way, on a number of elevated platforms, to admire the natural vegetation, birdlife and the views of the forest floor below. Each section of the trail varies in length from 70 to 230m, linking a total of 10 platforms along the 1.2km trail.  The other fun-packed adventure activity offered by Skyway Trails is the Rope Adventure Park. Here you can enjoy a unique and fun-packed experience, with two courses and 34 exciting obstacles – including balancing beams, rope bridges, swings and more – ending on a 50m zipline. (function(d, s, id) {  var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];  if (d.getElementById(id)) return;  js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;  js.src = 'https://connect.facebook.net/en_GB/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v3.0';  fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);}(document, 'script', 'facebook-jssdk')); Enjoy family fun, corporate fun days or team-building events. Discount offered for groups of six or more. Tour groups are welcome and there is ample safe parking.  Skyway Trails Adventure Centre is based at Perry’s Bridge Lifestyle Centre in Hazyview. For more information and to book, visit www.skywaytrails.com, email info@skywaytrails.com or contact 082 825 0209. (function(d, s, id) {  var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];  if (d.getElementById(id)) return;  js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;  js.src = 'https://connect.facebook.net/en_GB/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v3.0';  fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);}(document, 'script', 'facebook-jssdk'));